# Topic Page Contract (Required)

Every topic page MUST render two primary tabs/sections:
A) THEORY (detailed)
B) PRACTICE (interactive)

## A) THEORY must include (minimum headings)
- What you will learn
- Prerequisites (light)
- Mental model (simple first, then deep)
- Core concepts
- Design process (step-by-step)
- Trade-offs (table)
- Common mistakes & how to avoid
- Mini case study (realistic)
- Interview Q&A
- References (must map to key claims)

## B) PRACTICE must include (minimum)
- Interactive demo (controls + visualization)
- Side-by-side compare when relevant
- Timeline / event log (“what happened”)
- Guided steps mode (step-by-step)
- Hands-on task + solution reveal
